boto3 (1.40.61-0ubuntu1~ppa1~noble1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Initial packaging of boto3 1.40.61 for the Avalan PPA.
  * Transitive runtime dep of aiobotocore's [boto3] extra
    (Avalan's `vendors` extra, reached via aioboto3). Noble ships
    1.34.46+dfsg and the Debian snapshot pool has no version in
    aiobotocore's `>= 1.40.46, < 1.40.62` window; pinned from
    the upstream PyPI sdist at 1.40.61, the top of the window.
  * No source patches required: upstream's setup.py is the sole
    build entry point and Noble's setuptools 68 accepts it as-is.

 -- Avalan Packaging Team <avalan@avalan.ai>  Wed, 20 May 2026 11:30:00 -0300
